03:22:24 INFO    run_stage      interactions_rationale: We implemented EMI_to_Salary_Ratio because Total_EMI_per_month (MI=0.5471) and Monthly_Inhand_Salary (MI=0.5187) carry high, independent signal; their ratio is hypothesized to exceed MI>0.55 per EDA and capture debt burden relative to income. We also added Interest_Rate_Delay_Product to capture compounding credit risk: Interest_Rate (MI=0.1705) × Delay_from_due_date (MI=0.1215) should reveal nonlinear severity missed by linear F-statistics.
